name: Mia Sable Pin-Up Aluminum Water Bottle (Red)
description:
This pretty water bottle with original pin-up art portraying Mia Sable by Monte Moore, is eco-friendly & comes with 2 different tops! It will help keep you healthy and glowingly gorgeous as only good old fashioned hydration can.

Eco-Friendly
20oz/.6L Aluminum
Recyclable & Reusable
Hand Wash/Air Dry (Not suitable for carbonated drinks, hot liquids, milk, or alcohol)
Features 2 screw-tops: Hiking Snap Hook & Flip-Top Sipper
Diameter 2.8"
Height 8.25"

name: Mia Sable Pin-Up Tote (Red)
description:
This glamorous canvas tote with original pin-up art portraying Mia Sable by Monte Moore, is also large, strong, and perfectly shaped for everyday use. It will easily haul your high heels, hair spray... or you know... groceries, books, beach towels, baby supplies, or whatever else you desire! 

Eco-Friendly
100% Heavyweight Cotton Canvas 
30" Handles 
Gusseted bottom 
Width 14.5"
Height 15.75"
Depth 6.25"
